== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavukiye i Cape Town, muri Afurika y'Epfo. <ref>https://elcinema.com/en/person/2009428/</ref> Yakoraga i Londres, akora umwuga wo kwakira abashyitsi. Ariko, nyuma yaje kwimurirwa mu gukina amashusho. Yize rero arangiza muri CityVarsity School of Media Studies, Cape Town. Hanyuma yize muri Creative Arts College, kugirango arangize Impamyabumenyi yo gukina Kamera.<ref>https://www.imdb.com/name/nm2440022/bio</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Ishyaka rye ryo gukina ryaje ubwo yitabiraga amakinamico i Cape Town ndetse na Festival ya Grahamstown<ref>https://podcastaddict.com/podcast/2848710</ref>. Garth yaremye Mugaragaza ye gukinira mu 1993 na benshi muri [[Afurika y'Epfo]] ''mayaruka''  serial. Muri iyi filimi, yagize uruhare ruto rwa 'Jacques Venter<ref>https://hellhorror.com/movies/8-movie-6877.html</ref>'. Muri 2005, yakinnye muri mini-seri, ''Triangle'' iyobowe na Craid R Baxley. Hanyuma yakoze uruhare rukunzwe 'Pvt. Slug Skinner 'muri 2008 yerekanwe kuri videwo ya ''Starship Troopers 3: Marauder''<ref>https://gta.fandom.com/wiki/Garth_Breytenbach</ref> . Kuva mu 2014, yagaragaye kuri filimi rusange akina na ''Black Sails'' nyuma muri ''Deutschland 86'' (2018). <ref name="spling">http://www.spling.co.za/interviews/top-10-movies-with-garth-breytenbach</ref>

Muri 2017, yakinnye muri mini-serie ya ''Madiba'' na firime ''Beyond The River''. Icyakora uruhare rwe rwamamaye cyane muri 2017 rwanyuze muri firime yamafirime yuburengerazuba bwa [[Afrika yepfo]] 5 ''Fingers For Marseilles'' hamwe ninshingano 'Officer De Vries'. Muri 2013, yagaragaye kuri film ''Long Walk to Freedom'' ahanganye na Idris Elba. <ref>https://en.notrecinema.com/communaute/stars/stars.php3?staridx=79697</ref> Muri 2018, yakinnye nka 'Ajax', umurwanyi w'Ubugereki muri BBC na Netflix mini-seriyeri ''Troy: Fall Of A City'' (2018).<ref>https://purplebullent.com/amy_actor/garth-breytenbach/</ref>

Azwiho kandi gukina amakinamico yamateka nka ''Mandela:Long Walk to Freedom'', ''Winnie Mandela'', ''Verraaiers'' and ''Goodbye Bafana'' . Usibye uruhare rukomeye, Garth yanagaragaye mu nshingano zo gusetsa, cyane cyane muri seriveri ya ''Hammerhead TV'', irimo abakinnyi bazwi cyane Bevan Cullinan, Brendan Jack na Chris Forrest <ref>http://www.spling.co.za/interviews/top-10-movies-with-garth-breytenbach</ref>

